296
00:34:45,140 --> 00:34:48,780
Now welcome Mr. Shaojia to present the award to Xiang Zeyi

297
00:34:50,300 --> 00:34:50,900
Please

298
00:34:52,300 --> 00:34:55,020
Thank the organizing committee for giving me this award

299
00:34:57,580 --> 00:35:03,900
Actually I'm not here for this award today

300
00:35:08,780 --> 00:35:11,100
Yezi, I like you

301
00:35:51,620 --> 00:35:52,300
Daniao

302
00:35:57,900 --> 00:35:58,740
Why are you here?

303
00:36:03,180 --> 00:36:04,580
What's this?

304
00:36:06,580 --> 00:36:08,260
It's in your bag

305
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:09,580
How would I know what it is?

306
00:36:09,940 --> 00:36:11,220
I haven't told you yet

307
00:36:11,580 --> 00:36:13,060
How do you know it's from my bag?

308
00:36:15,020 --> 00:36:16,260
Are you tricking me?

309
00:36:17,900 --> 00:36:19,940
You want me to ask you, so you put it in my bag, right?

310
00:36:23,540 --> 00:36:25,500
Leniency to those who confess

311
00:36:25,700 --> 00:36:26,700
Tell me honestly

312
00:36:27,100 --> 00:36:28,180
Wait a moment

313
00:36:41,460 --> 00:36:42,780
You may do what you like

314
00:37:44,540 --> 00:37:45,300
Mom

315
00:37:48,580 --> 00:37:50,020
Calm down, mom

316
00:37:50,340 --> 00:37:51,300
Which hospital?

317
00:37:57,420 --> 00:37:58,540
Mom, what happened?

318
00:37:58,900 --> 00:38:00,100
I don't know

319
00:38:00,580 --> 00:38:02,380
He was alright when we were eating

320
00:38:02,540 --> 00:38:04,940
After the meal, he went out for a walk

321
00:38:05,420 --> 00:38:07,660
But some time later, he went back cupping his heart

322
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:11,700
Then he passed out without me realizing it

323
00:38:15,060 --> 00:38:17,500
How long has he been inside?

324
00:38:17,660 --> 00:38:18,700
What did the doctor say?

325
00:38:19,380 --> 00:38:21,740
He said nothing. Lin Sen is there

326
00:38:23,180 --> 00:38:26,460
Calm down. With Lin Sen there, father will be alright

327
00:38:28,860 --> 00:38:31,260
Yezi, your father has been quiet well

328
00:38:31,620 --> 00:38:32,500
But suddenly

329
00:38:33,980 --> 00:38:35,020
What should I do?

330
00:38:35,380 --> 00:38:36,420
Dad will be alright

331
00:38:36,860 --> 00:38:37,740
Believe me, mom

332
00:38:38,340 --> 00:38:39,460
Let's have a seat over there

333
00:38:40,180 --> 00:38:40,680
Here

334
00:39:12,500 --> 00:39:13,980
Why does it take such a long time?

335
00:39:14,340 --> 00:39:15,220
Anything wrong?

336
00:39:38,380 --> 00:39:41,780
Yezi, are you calling Zhuzi?

337
00:39:44,580 --> 00:39:45,140
No

338
00:40:07,780 --> 00:40:10,340
Lin Sen called me just now

339
00:40:11,300 --> 00:40:14,420
He said he had already arranged a ward for your father

340
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:16,660
And he would do surgery by himself

341
00:40:17,460 --> 00:40:20,540
He said he would save your father certainly

342
00:40:26,220 --> 00:40:27,260
I mean

343
00:40:28,500 --> 00:40:32,180
You are our only daughter

344
00:40:33,380 --> 00:40:35,980
We hope you will marry a good man

345
00:40:36,940 --> 00:40:40,580
So that you won't be alone when we pass away

346
00:40:42,820 --> 00:40:45,900
Mom, it's not a right time to say it now

347
00:40:46,860 --> 00:40:50,220
I know I have mentioned it for too many time

348
00:40:50,820 --> 00:40:51,820
You got tired of it

349
00:40:52,220 --> 00:40:53,540
But now

350
00:40:53,820 --> 00:40:56,020
Your father suddenly gets ill

351
00:40:56,340 --> 00:40:58,540
You know sometimes things change in a sudden

352
00:41:00,180 --> 00:41:01,700
I want to tell you that

353
00:41:02,020 --> 00:41:06,020
If a man loves you, he will love all people around you

354
00:41:06,460 --> 00:41:09,180
Then he is a right man to depend on

355
00:41:10,460 --> 00:41:13,940
Yezi, you need to cherish him

356
00:41:17,820 --> 00:41:18,860
I know, mom

357
00:41:21,100 --> 00:41:21,860
He is out

358
00:41:25,900 --> 00:41:26,980
How's my father?

359
00:41:27,340 --> 00:41:28,300
He is alright now

360
00:41:28,460 --> 00:41:29,340
But he needs a good rest

361
00:41:30,260 --> 00:41:31,220
Thank you

362
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:36,460
Don't worry

363
00:41:39,860 --> 00:41:40,380
Let's go

364
00:41:50,180 --> 00:41:50,900
What's up?

365
00:41:51,060 --> 00:41:53,380
Yezi's father has got a sudden heart attack

366
00:41:53,740 --> 00:41:54,900
And he is rescued in a hospital now

367
00:41:55,620 --> 00:41:56,340
How is he?

368
00:41:56,700 --> 00:41:57,540
I don't know

369
00:41:57,700 --> 00:41:59,620
Ask Yezi if you want to know

370
00:41:59,820 --> 00:42:00,320
Daniao

371
00:42:00,700 --> 00:42:01,220
Hey
